title: FEB 09 2022 - HOMELAND SECURITY: QUESTIONING ELECTIONS OR COVID IS DOMESTIC TERRORISM
description:
Homeland security released a statement updating domestic terrorist threat classifications to include conspiracies around the elections and COVID misinformation, Canada’s Premier Kenney of Alberta announces partial end to mandates amid trucker potests, meanwhile the U.S. Inspector General opens up an investigation on Capitol police who may be spying on members of congress, and a jury trial has been ordered for CNN’s Don Lemon after allegations of sexual assault. 




Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
